Say '''Balangkayan''' et kumalima ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Eastern Samar]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 9,046 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 207.05 sq. km. Sikato et walad alenleneg ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6801.	
															
